title: I Really Didn’t Want to Be the Savior - Novel Updates
tags: Male Protagonist   Nationalism   Racism   Slow Romance   Time Travel
author: 火中物
description: Eyes opened, crossing the thousand-year gate. When my eyes are closed, reality is still poorer than that. Chen Feng, a porter who travels through time and space with his life. From carrying songs, movies, various entertainment works to carrying various future technologies. Originally, he only wanted to be a porter who would eat and wait to die to enjoy life, but he did not expect that every time he moved technology, it would cause a technological explosion after a thousand years. Each of his actions will change the course of the next thousand years of history. Moving, he moved himself into the savior.>
